Socratis Otto https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Socratis_Otto 0 Socratis Otto is an Australian film, theatre and television actor. He is best known for his roles in television series Young Lions as Justin Carmody, Home and Away as Robert Robertson, and Wentworth as Maxine Conway.
